## đź“‹ Como Importar no n8n

1. Abra o n8n (https://app.n8n.cloud ou self-hosted)
2. Clique em **Workflows** â†’ **Import from JSON**
3. Cole o JSON acima
4. Configure as **credenciais** necessĂˇrias:
   - PostgreSQL (banco do CRM)
   - SMTP (e-mail)
   - Slack (webhook)
5. **Ative** o workflow
6. Copie a URL do webhook (ex: `https://seu-n8n.com/webhook/lead-capture`)

